I think the key here is that you use Whatever works for you--I Do know that
when you go to a "Tire Shoppe" or where-ever you buy your tires.-  Always
ask "What is the BEST Deal on a set of tires"! and mention the size you
want--This always works for me.--As a lot of "Tire Shoppes" Do carry, one or
two, sets of 4 tires
that they may have just a few of! Ergo you can cut yourself a deal., TWWM,
